column1: ## Initial set of words come from Mathematica with usage frequency.
## These have been augmented with Linux dictionary words: /usr/share/dict/words.
## The additional words have been filtered removing: words that end in "s";
## words with accents; and words with a capital letter.
## These additional words have been assigned the frequency of 1.0e-9 (lower than any of the Mathematica word frequencies).
